OL,3,CSwansea sets sights on green energy
OL,4,Cfuture as 250 jobs created
OL,6,FA Swansea-based company has recruited
OL,7,F250 new staff following the opening of
OL,8,Ftwo new offices on the city's
OL,9,Fwaterfront last year.
OL,11,FConsumer Energy Solutions, which
OL,12,Fprovides heating and insulation
OL,13,Fservices to help reduce the carbon
OL,14,Ffootprint of properties, has grown its
OL,15,Fworkforce to more than 700 staff.
OL,17,FManaging Director Lewis John said: "We
OL,18,Fare deeply committed to fostering
OL,19,Feconomic growth and prosperity in the
OL,20,Fregions where we operate."
