OL,3,CSwansea sets sights on green energy
OL,4,Cfuture as 250 jobs created
OL,6,FIt's one of a cluster of recent
OL,7,Fdevelopments and plans in a city which
OL,8,Fis pitching itself as a green energy
OL,9,Fhub.
OL,11,FIn Gowerton, consultation is open on a
OL,12,Fnew solar energy scheme which would
OL,13,Faim to power up to 11,500 homes in
OL,14,FSouth Wales each year.
OL,16,FThe planning application for Parc
OL,17,FSolar Caenewydd at the Penyfodau Fawr
OL,18,FFarm site has been submitted to Welsh
OL,19,FMinisters.
