OL,3,CSwansea sets sights on green energy
OL,4,Cfuture as 250 jobs created
OL,6,FSwansea Council's long-standing plans
OL,7,Ffor a renewable energy project in the
OL,8,Fport area took a step forward this
OL,9,Fmonth after receiving money from the
OL,10,FUK Government to explore how to use
OL,11,Fexcess heat from a data centre that
OL,12,Fwould form part of the development to
OL,13,Fwarm buildings in the city.
OL,15,FThe #4bn renewable energy project,
OL,16,Fnamed 'Blue Eden', is set to include a
OL,17,Ftidal lagoon, high-tech battery
OL,18,Fmanufacturing centre and an oceanic
OL,19,Fand climate research centre.
