OL,7,Fleader said: "We're all aware of the
OL,8,Fimpact of climate change and the
OL,9,Fimportance of taking steps to reduce
OL,10,Fits effects on us and future
OL,11,Fgenerations.
OL,13,FPlans for a tidal lagoon in Swansea,
OL,14,Fhowever, . In 2013, proposals were put
OL,15,Fforward that would generate enough
OL,16,Fenergy for 120,000 homes. The plans
OL,17,Fwere scrapped in 2018 by the UK
OL,18,FGovernment citing the high cost of the
OL,19,Fenergy produced.
